    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Carried Away</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Judith Noelle Lamb letter on Corby Kummer's Aug 30 article on bottled water; photo (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>I couldn't help smiling through most of Kummer's article, and bought my New York Times with companion purchases of Evian water and Yoplait yogurt, cultural hangovers from trips to France to visit a high-school pen pal. Sadly, the smile disappeared from my face when Kummer told us he used his bare hands to drink water from Panna's source -- without regard for the consequences. Was his ''audacity'' worth the possibility of contamination?</p>
        <p>Judith Noelle Lamb  Boston</p>
      </block>
